query: SELECT MIN(cn1.name) AS first_company, MIN(cn2.name) AS second_company, MIN(mi_idx1.info) AS first_rating, MIN(mi_idx2.info) AS second_rating, MIN(t1.title) AS first_movie, MIN(t2.title) AS second_movie FROM company_name AS cn1, company_name AS cn2, info_type AS it1, info_type AS it2, kind_type AS kt1, kind_type AS kt2, link_type AS lt, movie_companies AS mc1, movie_companies AS mc2, movie_info_idx AS mi_idx1, movie_info_idx AS mi_idx2, movie_link AS ml, title AS t1, title AS t2 WHERE lt.id = ml.link_type_id AND t1.id = ml.movie_id AND t2.id = ml.linked_movie_id AND it1.id = mi_idx1.info_type_id AND t1.id = mi_idx1.movie_id AND kt1.id = t1.kind_id AND cn1.id = mc1.company_id AND t1.id = mc1.movie_id AND ml.movie_id = mi_idx1.movie_id AND ml.movie_id = mc1.movie_id AND mi_idx1.movie_id = mc1.movie_id AND it2.id = mi_idx2.info_type_id AND t2.id = mi_idx2.movie_id AND kt2.id = t2.kind_id AND cn2.id = mc2.company_id AND t2.id = mc2.movie_id AND ml.linked_movie_id = mi_idx2.movie_id AND ml.linked_movie_id = mc2.movie_id AND mi_idx2.movie_id = mc2.movie_id AND (t2.title like '%house%' OR t2.title like '%suit%' OR t2.title like '%star%' OR t2.title like '%ship%') AND mc2.note not like '%Mexico%' AND mc2.note not like '%India%' AND mc2.note not like '%Portugal%' AND mc2.note not like '%Sweden%' AND mc2.note not like '%France%' AND mc1.note not like '%Australia%' AND mc1.note not like '%Germany%' AND mc1.note not like '%China%' AND mc1.note not like '%Japan%' AND it2.info not in ('height','rating','magazine cover photo','LD number','LD picture format','weekend gross','bottom 10 rank','LD number of sides','death notes','LD status of availablility','nick names','genres','LD certification','LD production country','mpaa') AND kt1.kind in ('movie','tv movie','episode','tv series','video game','tv mini series') AND kt2.kind not in ('tv mini series','tv movie','video game','episode','tv series','video movie') AND (cn2.name like '%Studio Ghibli%' OR cn2.name like '%A24%' OR cn2.name like '%Focus Features%' OR cn2.name like '%Legendary%') AND mi_idx1.info < '6.0' AND lt.link not in ('follows','featured in','spin off from','referenced in','followed by','references','features','similar to','edited into','version of','spoofs','unknown link','spoofed in','edited from','remade as') AND t1.production_year > 2008 AND t1.production_year < 2010 AND (t1.title like '%island%' OR t1.title like '%spell%' OR t1.title like '%light%')
